mac.init(new SecretKeySpec(HMAC_KEY, "HmacSHA256"));
if (!MessageDigest.isEqual(receivedHmac, mac.doFinal(payload))) {
    throw new SecurityException("Tampered payload");
}
```

2. **JEP 290 Deserialization Filters** - Whitelist allowed classes before instantiation:
```java
