**Additional Protections**:
- **Trusted proxy configuration**: Only trusts X-Forwarded-For from configured reverse proxy IPs, preventing IP spoofing attacks
- **Timing-safe comparisons**: Uses `hash_equals()` for all security-sensitive string comparisons to prevent timing attacks
- **Argon2ID password hashing**: Modern memory-hard algorithm with automatic rehashing on login when algorithm changes
- **Comprehensive audit logging**: All events logged to database AND syslog for SIEM integration
- **Real-time security alerts**: Slack/email notifications for lockouts and suspicious activity
- **Session timeout and activity tracking**: Auto-logout after 30 minutes of inactivity
