**Defense in Depth Layers**:

1. **Source Allowlisting**: Only fetch content from pre-approved domains
```javascript
if (!this.config.allowedDomains.includes(parsedUrl.hostname)) {
  throw new Error('Content source not allowed');
}
```

2. **Content Sanitization**: Remove HTML, scripts, and injection patterns from external data
```javascript
const dangerousPatterns = [
